          h1 Types, tokens and morphology
        section
          h2 Types and tokens
          ul
            li <b>Tokens</b> refer to the individual words in the text
            li <b>Types</b> are the distinct words we see in the text
          div(class="center")
            p 
              em I know that this is simple
            p 6 <b>Tokens</b>, 5 <b>Types</b>
        section
