              th cars
              th car
              th car
            tr
              th caring
              th care
              th car
            tr
              th taught
              th teach
              th taught (!?)
          p Stemming is not linguistically motivated
        section
          h2 Inflection and Derivation
          ul 
            li Inflection captures the lemma and the change that has happened to it
            ul
              li writing = write + PRESENT + PROGRESSIVE
            li Derivation is how new words are formed
            ul
              li agreement = agree + MENT
